text: Feeding Frenzy is a arcade video game developed and published by PopCap Games. It involves fish eating other fish. The game was the 17th most popular Xbox Live Arcade title for 2006. == References == Category:2004 video games Category:Arcade games Category:Casual games Category:Flash games Category:MacOS games Category:Mobile games Category:Single-player video games Category:Video games about fish Category:Video games developed in the United States Category:Windows games Category:Xbox 360 Live Arcade games
